{"word":"ἐπερωτάω","slug":"ἐπερωτάω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἐπερωτάω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐπί\">ἐπί</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐρωτάω\">ἐρωτάω</a></el>]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> ‘put a question to’, <b>ask <a href='B:470 12:10'>Mt 12:10</a>; <a href='B:480 5:9'>Mk 5:9</a>; <a href='B:480 8:23'>8:23</a>; <a href='B:480 11:29'>11:29</a>; <a href='B:490 22:64'>Lk 22:64</a>; <a href='B:500 9:23'>J 9:23</a>; <a href='B:530 14:35'>1 Cor 14:35</a>;</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> <b><a href='B:510 23:34'>Ac 23:34</a>;</b> of formal interrogation <b><a href='B:470 27:11'>Mt 27:11</a>; <a href='B:480 15:2'>Mk 15:2</a>; <a href='B:510 5:27'>Ac 5:27</a>.</b> W. double <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ acc.\">acc.</a> <el>ἐ. αὐτὸν τ. παραβολήν</el> they asked him about the parable<b> <a href='B:480 7:17'>Mk 7:17</a>. <p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> ‘make a request’, <b>ask for <a href='B:470 16:1'>Mt 16:1</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐπέρχομαι\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐπερώτημα\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}